cs.AI, cs.HC, cs.LG, cs.MA, cs.RO 

This paper is primarily focused on the intersection of artificial intelligence and human-computer interaction, specifically on the ability of AI agents to coordinate with humans. Therefore, cs.AI and cs.HC are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses machine learning algorithms such as self-play and population-based training, which fall under cs.LG. The use of a planning algorithm falls under cs.MA, and the discussion of the Overcooked game environment falls under cs.RO.
